defs.name: full_docs
defs.docs:
Include all documentation for items. (If `false`, only includes the
 summary (first paragraph) for each item).

defs.name: pub_only
defs.docs:
If true only includes data for public items in a crate (useful for
 library crates).

defs.name: distro_crate
defs.docs: True if and only if the analysed crate is part of the standard Rust distro.
